#styleguide

  h1 UI Styleguide
  p Styleguide for UI elements such as forms and tables
  
  h2 Tabular data
  p Tables should be used when displaying tabular data. The thead, tfoot and tbody elements enable you to group rows within each a table.
  p If you use these elements, you must use every element. They should appear in this order: thead, tfoot and tbody, so that browsers can render the foot before receiving all the data. You must use these tags within the table element.
  
  table
    caption The Very Best Eggnog
    colgroup
      col style="width:15em;"
      col style="width:6em;"
      col style="width:6em;"
    thead
      tr
        th scope="col"
          | Ingredients
