  h2 Forms
  p Forms can be used when you wish to collect data from users. The fieldset element enables you to group related fields within a form, and each one should contain a corresponding legend. The label element ensures field descriptions are associated with their corresponding form widgets.
  
  form action="#"
    fieldset
      legend Legend
      div
        label for="text"
          | Text input 
        input id="text" type="text"
        em Note about this field 
      div
        label for="password"
          | Password 
        input id="password" type="password"
        em Note about this field 
      div
        label for="url"
          | Web Address 
        input id="url" type="url"
        em Note about this field 
      div
        label for="email"
          | Email Address 
        input id="email" type="email"
        em Note about this field
      div
        label for="textarea"
          | Text Area 
        textarea id="textarea" rows="8" cols="48"
        em Note about this field 
      div
        label for="email"
          | Email Address 
        input id="email" type="email"
        em Note about this field
      div
        label for="checkbox"
          | Single Checkbox 
        label for="checkbox" class="check"
          input id="checkbox" type="checkbox" class="checkbox"
